---
title: Roasted Garlic Herb Penne with Asparagus, Tomatoes, and Crispy Capers
description: The week just isn’t complete without a pasta night. If you agree (and how could you not?), you’re in luck! Our chefs put together a dish that’s sure to curb the most ferocious of carb cravings. In it, you’ll find bites of penne studded with tender asparagus, fresh tomatoes, and swirled with garlic herb butter. The dish is finished with a sprinkle of nutty Parmesan and your new secret culinary weapon: crispy capers. They’re crunchy, briny, and take just seconds to make. These buds really shine atop pasta, but add them to just about any dish for a crispy treat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/2019-w07-r10-67be6056.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/2019-w07-r10-5c2a61e7e3f33954af7b8082-81320e02.pdf
time required: 25 minutes
cuisine: North America
servings: 2
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/roasted-garlic-herb-penne-5c2a61e7e3f33954af7b8082
